subsection.def:
election (選舉) has
                the same meaning as in section 3(1) of the Legislative Council Ordinance
                    (Cap. 542);

elector (選民) has the
                same meaning as in section 3(1) of the Legislative Council Ordinance
                    (Cap. 542);

functional constituency (功能界別) has the same meaning as in section
                    3(1) of the Legislative Council Ordinance (Cap.
                    542);

geographical constituency (地方選區) has the same meaning as in section
                    3(1) of the Legislative Council Ordinance (Cap.
                    542);

